## Phase 4: Planned Data Sources & Signals  

### Economic Indicators  
- **World Bank – Food Price Index:** Food affordability stress  
- **World Bank – Poverty & Consumption:** Dietary access constraints  

### Health & Nutrition Indicators  
- **WHO (GHO):** Anemia prevalence (women, age-specific)  
- **UNICEF (DHS / MICS):** Stunting and wasting in children  
- **FAO:** National nutrient availability  

### Digital Behavioral Signals  
- **Google Trends:** “fatigue”, “hair loss” as early symptom proxies  
- **Google Trends:** “iron deficiency” as awareness escalation  

