Micronutrient deficiency is not a data-scarcity problem—it is a **signal-extraction problem**.

The Silent Hunger Discovery Engine integrates:
- Economic stress signals  
- Population-level nutrition indicators  
- Digital behavioral proxies  

to detect rising nutritional risk **before clinical failure occurs**.

